After teaming up with @Neutrogena to introduce you to their new Stubborn Acne & Marks treatments, I received several DM questions regarding reasons behind acne, as well as post-acne marks. This is why I wanted to record a video, for all of you who still doubts about how to treat this common skin issue. Let me know in the comments below if you have any other questions. 👩‍⚕️ #Neutrogena_Partner 

Check out the products I recommend:
👉🏻 Neutrogena Stubborn Acne AM treatment – With micronized 2.5% Benzoyl Peroxide which helps kill acne causing bacteria
👉🏻 Neutrogena Stubborn Marks PM treatment with Retinol SA – Visibly reduces the look of post-acne marks 
👉🏻 Neutrogena SkinClearing Makeup line – This line treats blemishes, helps prevent breakouts, control shine and provides natural coverage

Warm weather means dealing with heat, humidity and sunlight, which can cause clogged pores, age spots, and sometimes even skin cancer (because of the accumulation of sun exposure and if you are not vigilant about protecting your skin)  Some tips for skin care in hot weather are: -moisturize the skin but with thinner products
-increase your water intake
-increase your exfoliation times especially if its humid 
-use a humidifier if the weather is dry and hot
-adjust your cleanser to one with less alcohol if its dry outside.
